’Щ@a0a0d7f2936f72bb828ee3be0b46acc902271522e00e165328b98dc65eecc1b8ЩчTitle: title: view files
Path: Examples
Content:
View the files registered in Nushell's EngineState memory.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> view files


```
View how Nushell was originally invoked.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> view files | get 0


```
